A Python OMR  (Optical Mark Reader) script. Made with OpenCV, pytesseract and pdf2image libraries.

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

1. Clone the repository and acess directory.
git clone git clone https://github.com/fabionaves/readeromr/
cd readeromr

2. Create envoriment and load it.
python3 -m venv env
source env/bin/activate

3. Install readeromr requeriments.
pip install wheel
pip install -r requeriments.txt

4. Install poppler.
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install -y poppler-utils


4. Configure template.ini file.
PATH = 
POPPLER_PATH = 
IMG_PATH = 

5. Script Usage
python readeromr.py -f example200dpiMono.pdf -q 90 -t template.ini